bpp/descriptor.name: Eatiko Technologies Private Limited
bpp/descriptor.short_desc: Your trusted partner for fast and reliable food delivery
bpp/descriptor.long_desc: Eatiko is a leading food delivery service connecting customers with a wide range of restaurants, local eateries, and grocery stores across the region. With a focus on convenience, quality, and speed, Eatiko enables customers to order meals, groceries, and other essentials from nearby vendors with ease.
